Feature: User-Friendly Claim Submission Interface

  In order to submit claims easily
  As a user
  I need a user-friendly interface that guides me through the process

  Scenario: Using the user-friendly interface for claim submission
    Given I am logged in as a user
    When I navigate to the claim submission section
    And follow the step-by-step instructions
    Then I should be able to submit my claim without difficulties
    And receive confirmation of successful submission

  Scenario: Editing a submitted claim
    Given I have submitted a claim
    When I navigate to the submitted claims section
    And select the claim to edit
    Then I should be able to modify the details
    And resubmit the updated claim with confirmation
